{"tid":1761428,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[冇走數][有圖][義助Telegram Booth 報告]","createTime":"2019-11-29T02:19:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T02:31:27.000Z","uid":305022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"44ae1730d86c5a18e0e6e4083783e9683d727368","tid":1761428,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:19:28.000Z","msg":"[當抗爭變成工作][有圖]黃絲經濟圈之進化永動機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1744805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1744805</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S3h7eyf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS3h7eyf.jpg&h=e6228c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次開POST到而家，終於可以義助到一班手足去攪TG booth，佢地全程主導，為左保護手足就唔貼人喇，<br />\n以下有幾點想分享。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1. 將Telegram Channel印QR code喺紙上面貼喺牆上面，就算佢哋得幾個人，其他冇人招呼嘅街坊，都可以影相或者scan QR code<br />\n<br />\n2.其實好多中年人嘅人佢哋冇用Telegram或者連登唔知道幾時有活動，所以幫佢哋追蹤某啲Channel例如日程表好有用<br />\n<br />\n3. 大家都好主動，唔會偷懶而且有耐性，會同街坊主動傾計，有時有啲深黃既可以幫佢地追蹤助養群或者物資組<br />\n<br />\n4. 傾完計先發現佢哋走得比較前，其實我覺得勇武嘅定義就係，唔係只勇氣，而係指願意付出幾多時間，前面又係佢，做地區工作又喺佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 大家都覺得Telegram攤位值得大搞，因為例如好似放映會，連儂牆都係一啲資訊性嘅嘢，但未必可以好具體咁增加到群眾嘅行動力。而透過同街坊溝通，幫佢哋入唔同嘅Channel例如物資組助養群就可以將民意轉化為行動力。<br />\n<br />\n希望各位金主同和理非攪多啲類似既活動，提供多元既平台比自己人，以上報告完畢。<br />\n<br />\n最後發下晦氣先，P牌POST無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34670fd973a82e7a5ef0e86fa38d7666b7d2f84e","tid":1761428,"uid":60408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:24:43.000Z","msg":"幫你推!"},{"pid":"4a328f55bf27d7a208eb4637f655a5006d2f34ab","tid":1761428,"uid":244546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:26:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"eae28faf45c20a85e2374bb2afb1fb043dd3ffa5","tid":1761428,"uid":305022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T02:31:27.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁但推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}